{"type": "article", "id": 20359, "title": "钻石灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-07T07:36:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152232zLguDtcb7yM09wSO.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是英国照明公司 The Electrical Shop 推出的 Diamond Cage，将圆形灯泡放在了钻石结构的灯罩里。带有尖锐表面的灯罩和圆形灯泡产生了对比，小巧而有雕塑感。灯罩上没有玻璃，所以很轻，可以通过电线挂起来，或者直接放在桌面上。这盏灯连接了不同颜色的电线，最近推出了黑枪色，售价 79 英镑起，<a href=\"http://www.the-electrical-shop.co.uk/shop?category=Gunmetal\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152230vnO8wlsm2ra3FLHQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152231qyeOQUBrEcghJP9C.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152231pzQ2RVrjd8nutg4B.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152231q6iACoDzhvb3GHfB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}